y, we find four potential members of a common proper\nmotion group with Albireo, though none anywhere as close by as the Albireo\ncomponents A to B.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Dec 2020 15:33:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 30 Dec 2020 16:05:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-20"}
