ing algorithms with\ndomain knowledge in the construction of recommendation systems for astronomy.\nOur code is publicly available at https://github.com/snad-space/zwad\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Dec 2020 12:06:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 2 Feb 2021 09:25:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-10"}
