 two quantities are linear functions of\nthe imposed electrical potential ; the tip displacement varies as the length\nsquare, and the blocking force is proportional to the width and inversely\nproportional to the length.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Dec 2020 11:36:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-08"}
