ions of\ndiffusion, exchange, and T1 and T2 NMR relaxation in static tissues, with a\npossibility to straightforwardly account for susceptibility-induced T2* effects\nand flow.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Dec 2020 04:20:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 10 Apr 2021 01:45:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-13"}
